First Fact
How dose the Air-Bag opens in the car?

Ans:- Car ke Stearing wheel or tires me speed sencers hote hai,
      ye sencers presure sencers se connected hote hai jo ki ek heating
      coil se connected hota hai,heating coil ke aage hirdogen gas hoti
      hai, accedent ke samai presure sencer heating coil ko activate
      kerte hai jo turant hi gas koo garam kerk airbag ko inflate deta hai
      jise accident me death or badi injuries ke chances come ker deta hai.

Second Fact
